    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 0}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 6
    TextStory: "C\xF4 t\xEDnh k\xEDch ho\u1EA1t Arts th\xEAm m\u1ED9t l\u1EA7n n\u1EEFa
      th\xEC b\u1ECB nh\u1EEFng s\u1EE3i d\xE2y m\xE0u tr\u1EAFng s\xE1ng lao ra
      tr\xF3i ch\u1EB7t tay v\xE0 c\u01A1 th\u1EC3 c\xF4 r\u1ED3i k\xE9o m\u1EA1nh
      v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa m\u1EB7t g\u01B0\u01A1ng l\u1EDBn."
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e70d4e77c490f1f449f2b6b225a8f6f2, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 0}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 3
    TextStory: "M\u1ECDi th\u1EE9 ch\xECm trong b\xF3ng t\u1ED1i s\xE2u th\u1EB3m,
      l\xFAc n\xE0y c\xF4 ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c r\u01A1i t\u1EF1 do trong
      kho\u1EA3ng kh\xF4ng v\xF4 t\u1EADn."
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e70d4e77c490f1f449f2b6b225a8f6f2, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 917811e49cf2b3048ab08ba81c62194e, type: 3}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 0
    TextStory: "C\u1EA3m gi\xE1c \u0111\xF3 khi\u1EBFn c\xF4 \u1EDBn l\u1EA1nh c\xF4
      c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng di chuy\u1EC3n c\u01A1 th\u1EC3 c\u1EE7a b\u1EA3n th\xE2n"
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e70d4e77c490f1f449f2b6b225a8f6f2, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 917811e49cf2b3048ab08ba81c62194e, type: 3}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 0
    TextStory: "Nh\u01B0ng \u0111\xE1p l\u1EA1i c\xF4 ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 s\u1EF1 b\u1EA5t
      l\u1EF1c c\u1EE7a t\u1EEBng b\u1ED9 ph\u1EADn tr\xEAn c\u01A1 th\u1EC3 m\xECnh
      c\u1EE9 nh\u01B0 th\u1EC3 m\u1ECDi gi\xE1c quan c\u1EE7a c\xF4 g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0
      qu\xEAn vi\u1EC7c ch\xFAng t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i"
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e70d4e77c490f1f449f2b6b225a8f6f2, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 917811e49cf2b3048ab08ba81c62194e, type: 3}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 0
    TextStory: "Ngay c\u1EA3 vi\u1EC7c h\xEDt th\u1EDF c\xF4 c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng c\u1EA3m
      th\u1EA5y g\xEC nh\u01B0 th\u1EC3 ngay t\u1EEB \u0111\u1EA7u vi\u1EC7c h\xEDt
      th\u1EDF ch\u01B0a bao gi\u1EDD t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i v\u1EADy"
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e70d4e77c490f1f449f2b6b225a8f6f2, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
    Background: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 917811e49cf2b3048ab08ba81c62194e, type: 3}
    textChoose: []
  - state: 0
    TextStory: "C\xF4 c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng nh\u1EAFm m\u1EAFt v\u1EDBi hy v\u1ECDng
      m\xECnh th\u1EADt s\u1EF1 \u0111ang nh\u1EAFm m\u1EAFt v\xE0 c\u1EA7u mong
      r\u1EB1ng \u0111\xE2y ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t gi\u1EA5c m\u01A1 "
    NameStory: Mint
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0892c8a07e913924b8f65601cd368d6a, type: 3}
    imgNV: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 62b83d5aa36e6574da31e65802ea68ce, type: 3}
